messages.message:
Do we have a list of emails and passwords for diff types of users used in cypress tests across environments?

I'm trying to find what the `CyUser.DEFAULT` is for aihub-uat

It's in this file: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/cebeb2d1a1a63e0ae0c0147f4244507bd5ecb361/webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked/cypress.config.js
The default user uses the `username` and `password` env vars
We should have that. I added a bunch for org admin/users in 1pass. I'll add the community users to 1pass as well
Added! You can search for "Cypress Jenkins" in 1pass for aihub-sandbox and uat envs; and search for "Cypress CI" for crafting-cyp sandbox
